comments.content: Looks like some sort of ultra compressed Impact for the roman and Nuptial Script for the script initials (way manipulated)

[Helvetica Ultra Compressed](http://web.archive.org/web/20110125184018/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/helvetica/ultra-compressed/) maybe squooshed or the stroke is affecting the look of it.
